item.content:encoded:
[spb_column width="1/3" el_position="first"] [spb_text_block padding_vertical="0" padding_horizontal="4" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]

Customer Service.

Call: +44 (0) 208 0000 000 Email: youremail@yourdomain.com Twitter: @SwiftIdeas
Returning an item?
Please include a note specifying whether you intend to return or exchange. Mail the item to: Apple Computer Inc 1 Infinite Loop Cupertino CA 95014 [/spb_text_block] [spb_blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block padding_vertical="0" padding_horizontal="4" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]
Drop us a line.
[contact-form-7 id="4" title="Contact form 1"] [/spb_text_block] [/spb_column] [spb_column width="2/3" el_position="last"] [spb_text_block padding_vertical="0" padding_horizontal="4" width="1/2" el_position="first"]

F.A.Q.

When will my order ship?
Orders in stock are usually shipped within 1–3 business days. For small goods, please allow up to 3–5 days for your order to go out.
What shipping methods do you use?
We primarily use USPS or UPS, however, make exceptions for stockists and bulk orders.
Where do you ship?
Almost everywhere. Email info@cardinal if you’re having trouble placing an order.
What if my tracking number doesn’t work?
Confirmation is sent when your shipping label is printed, please allow up to 12 hours for this information to update.
How long does it take for a refund to go through?
We will process your return as soon as we receive it, please allow 3–10 days for your bank account to update.
Do you take custom orders?
We are unable to make custom pieces for individuals most of the time, however, can accommodate special projects with larger quantities. Contact custom@cardinal.com for more information.
Where can I purchase your products?
All of our stockists are listed under “About” on the website.
How do I become a stockist?
If you would like to be considered, please email john@cardinal.com. Include a link to your website, other brands carried, pictures of your store and your “wish list”. We will review your store and respond within 1–3 days.
What if I’m experiencing issues with your website?
If you are having trouble checking out or other website issues please call us at: 0800 1234 567 or email us at info@cardinal.com. We will respond to you as quickly as possible.
Press inquiries?
For all press inquiries, please contact info@mcardinal.com. [/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block padding_vertical="0" padding_horizontal="4" width="1/2" el_position="last"]
